placed in the barrels.

01:09:56.456 --> 01:09:57.590
Maybe we can talk about this.

01:09:57.691 --> 01:09:59.292
We could buy him off you
fair and square.

01:09:59.392 --> 01:10:00.961
Nothing to talk about.

01:10:01.061 --> 01:10:02.495
