01:10:04.131 --> 01:10:05.733
Not my problem.

01:10:05.833 --> 01:10:06.901
Mac?

01:10:07.001 --> 01:10:09.369
Sorry, man. Nothing I can do.

01:10:09.469 --> 01:10:10.738
